Celia:  \F[10]\AA[F]That being said, we have to find the
last \c[14]cipher\c[0]!

Hayato:  That being said...\c[14]it might be better to give
up.

Hayato:  The fact that they're not even giving us a hint
means they never intended to give us the answer in the first
place.

Hayato:  Or another thing... \c[14]We don't know if that
cipher can really be used for escape\c[0].

Hayato:  We must not forget that this is a battle against
the main force of the \c[14]Demon King's army\c[0]....

Celia:  \F[15]\AA[F]........... (I, I've been honestly
collecting them, but....)

Celia:  \F[10]\AA[F](There's no proof that these numbers...
can really be used, right?)
Hayato:  Wh, what!? Directly into my brain....
Celia:  This voice... it can't be!
Anthurium:  Finally, my voice has reached you♡
addLog ハヤト「敵じゃない...の？」

Celia:  \F[3]\AA[F]Um... Didn't you return to the spirit
world?

Anthurium:  I intended to, but... It seems like some sort of
mechanism is preventing me from leaving this place.

Celia:  \F[37]\AA[F]What did you say... So even if we
hypothetically gathered the four-digit code.........

Hayato: So you're saying we can't escape unless Sadi undoes
the spell. The issue wasn't even about the code after
all....

Anthurium:  You're probably right. That's why Anthurium...
\c[14]was searching for the weapons storage room\c[0].

Anthurium:  The \c[14]storage room\c[0], which is
Anthurium's old haunt, is not affected by this spell....
That's why there should be a clue to escape there.

Celia:  \F\c[14]\AA[F]Hey, Hayato! You can handle that
\c[14]weapon\c[0], can't you? After all, you're the
\c[14]hero's younger brother\c[0]!

Hayato: ............I'm sorry, Celia. What do you mean by
'weapon'\c[0]?

Celia:  \F[10]\AA[F]Ah, yes. There were powerful weapons in
the church basement from the beginning, right? You, who have
been living in Variente, would know... right?
Hayato: {...Are you talking about the \c[14]Holy Sword\c[0]?

Celia:  \F[10]\AA[F]\c[14]Holy Sword\c[0]... It's definitely
strong, isn't it!! So, Anthurium! Have you found that room?

Anthurium:  Please come near me, Celia. I will use
[Teleport]....

Sadi:  ....Isn't that terrible, Anthurium♡ After I was so
kind to you...♡

Anthurium:  Master Sadi.......? This is bad! His
interference...!!
